{"tid":1708778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺最艱難嘅時刻 懇請咁多位手足重溫一下天琦嘅信","createTime":"2019-11-11T16:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T18:49:07.000Z","uid":121713,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1d9fd2a2821e1cf73c419b04b329b452e0dba8","tid":1708778,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"我希望你們能夠明白：本著對香港的熱愛，你們已展現了無比的勇氣，改寫了香港的歷史。當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39db9d9f502ba25ef43855ae3f551e7c5c46fae3","tid":1708778,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"5f30c22e5636ba3708b582d5038ea133d8c59c5e","tid":1708778,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"2888f828581b90f698b5a8ff9204d4fd75579501","tid":1708778,"uid":234899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4624c6f1a8447d191ebfaf4f20b06c4f0b34e5ed","tid":1708778,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e4872f2d647ca172a30debe1302ec4d7c55dd2a","tid":1708778,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7a70f9f46ea7407e088de3040e559802e22f8d","tid":1708778,"uid":333916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\